org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_Foundations.Time

Interface ClockType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClockTypeImpl

    public interface ClockType
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Clock Type'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Nature
    • Unit Type
    • Is Logical
    • Resol Attr
    • Max Val Attr
    • Offset Attr
    • Get Time
    • Set Time
    • Index To Value
    • Base Class

    See Also:
    TimePackage.getClockType()
